public boolean  (final String expectedXML){ boolean xmlIsSimilar=true; Diff difference=null; try { XMLUnit.setIgnoreAttributeOrder(true); XMLUnit.setIgnoreComments(true); XMLUnit.setIgnoreWhitespace(true); difference=new Diff(xmlDocument expectedXML); difference.overrideDifferenceListener(new DifferenceListener(){ @Override public int differenceFound( Difference difference){ if (excludedNodes.contains(difference.getControlNodeDetail().getNode().getLocalName())) return 1; else { return 0; } } @Override public void skippedComparison( Node node  Node node2){ } } ); xmlIsSimilar=difference.similar(); } catch ( Exception e) { xmlIsSimilar=false; LOGGER.info(e.getMessage()); } if (!xmlIsSimilar) { recordErrorMessage(difference); } return xmlIsSimilar; }
